name: The Red Sea
description: This Illustration I originally sketched on a dry erase board, in an attempt at recreating the original I was able to preserve a hint of my youthful arrogance & ended up creating a better piece. This is my interpretation Of Moses freeing the Israelites from bondage, parting the Red Sea & dropping it down upon the Egyptians. If you look closely there are men, horses & buggies being consumed by the waves as they crash down.
